msgid "Your sleep on the voyage home is fraught with nightmares. Upon returning to Arkham, you and the others bring the expedition's findings back to an elated Tillinghast. As you relay the events of the expedition to the collector, he turns each piece in hand, marveling at the ancient technology. \"You've done all I asked and more,\" he grins. \"Consider your debts annulled. And, of course, I'm more than happy to honor our original agreement.\""
msgstr ""

msgid "Your sleep on the voyage home is fraught with nightmares. Upon returning to Arkham, you and the others lay your few findings before Tillinghast. The antiquarian is furious when he sees you returned empty handed until Andy lays the obsidian slab he found in R'lyeh on his desk. Randall surveys it with a cold stare. \"I suppose this isâ€¦ adequate. Consider your debts annulled. And, despite the fact that you have brought almost <i>nothing</i> of value, I am obliged to honor our original agreement.\""
msgstr ""

